  Locus:
    Date: 19 June 2009
    Section: 43
---
Look, all worldly successes have their downside. The richer you become, the
more pride you have. The higher your rank, the bossier you act. The greater
your ambition, the more inconsiderate you are.

Success in the Dharma works differently. The better you become, the better
you become.
